description: Welcome to this charming 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo where timeless charm meets modern comfort in the heart of South Boston’s Andrew Square. This unit offers 700 square feet of intelligently designed living space, blending the character of a classic Boston building with the modern amenities of today. Step into a sun-filled open-concept layout featuring high ceilings, large windows, and hardwood floors that add warmth and personality. The combined living and dining space is accented with elegant crown molding and a gas fireplace, creating a cozy yet refined setting perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample storage that combines function with style. A private deck off the primary bedroom provides the ideal spot for morning coffee or casual gatherings with family and friends. The flexible second room, framed by French doors, is perfect for a nursery or home office.
